description: Wholly Frijoles is bringing Cleveland delicious and authentic Mexican street food with an innovative twist.The Wholly Frijoles Truck was born from the fast-casual Mexican taquería concept. The food is built upon traditional recipes and flavors to stimulate your palettes, and presented in an engaging environment to provide customers with a truly unique food experience. The Mexican and Latino cuisine is made with the freshest ingredients and spiced up with some of the most enticing flavors that have ever dazzled your taste-buds!
name: Wholly Frijoles Mexican street foods
